OL,3,C'Brink of famine': Why South Sudan's
OL,4,Cchildren are paying the price of war
OL,6,FITV News has travelled to a region in
OL,7,FSouth Sudan declared IPC5 -
OL,8,Fcatastrophic malnutrition. The only
OL,9,Fother place in the world with this
OL,10,Flevel of food insecurity is Gaza. The
OL,11,Fgovernor of the Upper Nile region says
OL,12,Fthey are close to a famine. Senior
OL,13,FInternational Correspondent John
OL,14,FIrvine has this special report
OL,16,FThe villages have been left to fend
OL,17,Ffor themselves, but can't.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
