OL,3,C'Brink of famine': Why South Sudan's
OL,4,Cchildren are paying the price of war
OL,6,FSouth Sudan is the world's youngest
OL,7,Fnation, but for 13 of the 15 years
OL,8,Fsince it gained independence in 2011,
OL,9,Fit has been blighted by civil war or
OL,10,Fstrife.
OL,12,FThe biggest tribe forms the rump of
OL,13,Fthe government, but there's continuous
OL,14,Ftension with other tribes and that
OL,15,Ffrequently leads to conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
