OL,3,C'Brink of famine': Why South Sudan's
OL,4,Cchildren are paying the price of war
OL,6,FUpper Nile state saw more violence
OL,7,Fback in February, and that is one of
OL,8,Fthe main drivers behind this crisis
OL,9,Fbecause the international aid agencies
OL,10,Fare no longer operating in the areas
OL,11,Faffected.
OL,13,FThose are the places we went to. Over
OL,14,Fthe years, they've become totally
OL,15,Freliant on aid, and now that it's no
OL,16,Flonger arriving, these communities are
OL,17,Fwithering.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
