OL,3,C'Brink of famine': Why South Sudan's
OL,4,Cchildren are paying the price of war
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FSo local nurses set up clinics to
OL,12,Freceive concerned mothers and their
OL,13,Fyoung, hungry children. They give them
OL,14,Fwhat medicines they can, then send
OL,15,Fthem home.
OL,17,FAnother big factor in the dwindling
OL,18,Faid supply across the state is cuts in
OL,19,Fthe aid budgets of rich nations like
OL,20,Fthe US and the UK. Cutbacks have
OL,21,Fconsequences that are visible here.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
